      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "type Questionaire {\n    question: Question;\n    prevQuestio: Question;\n    nextQuestion: Question;\n    \n}\n\ntype Question {\n    id: string;\n    emoji: string;\n    title: string;\n    options?: string[]; // radio, checkbox\n    acceptsMultiple: boolean;\n    text?: string; // input;\n    isRange: boolean;\n    isFirstStep: boolean;\n}\n",
